caption.p: Serum cytokine levels of IFN-γ, IL-2, IL-4, IL-6, IL-10, IL-12P40, MCP-1 and TNF-α were determined by multiplex magnetic bead assay in AG129 mice at 2 days after subcutaneous infection with 10 2 PFU of M-30 and S-27 CHIKV strains. Asterisks show significant differences by Kruskal-Wallis test (*) and by Mann–Whitney U-test (**), P < 0.05.
